name: 02 Memory Card - Ziggy the slippery
description: Expensive cigars are his favorite things that are always carried everywhere. Ziggy rules the black market in El Dorado, where many kinds of contraband such as white powder, auto parts, and illegal weapons are sold. Don't ever deal with a Weasel this time, because what you buy is not necessarily what you see. He is good at taking advantage of things and controlling them as desired.
